                <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="font-semibold text-base-900 mb-2">
                  Recommended: Official Xteink Website
                </Text>
                <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700 mb-3">
                  <a href="https://www.xteink.com/products/xteink-x4" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-500 hover:underline font-medium">
                    Xteink.com
                  </a> ‚Äì $69, fastest shipping (5‚Äì10 days to US/Europe if in stock).
                </Text>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-base-700 ml-4">
                  <li>Always check <strong>availability date</strong> on product page.</li>
                  <li>Full warranty support via <a href="mailto:support@xteink.com" class="text-accent-500 hover:underline">support@xteink.com</a>.</li>
                  <li>Ships with English firmware ready.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-base-100 border border-base-300 rounded-lg p-6 mb-4">
                <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="font-semibold text-base-900 mb-2">
                  Alternative: AliExpress/Cat3c Store
                </Text>
                <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
                  $38‚Äì$45 (saves $30), but <strong>20‚Äì28 days</strong> delivery. Often Chinese firmware (easily switched to English).
                </Text>
              </div>

              <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-600 italic">
                <strong>Tracking:</strong> Expect updates <strong>24‚Äì48 hours after fulfillment</strong>. No tracking during China warehouse processing is normal.
              </Text>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

