                  </Text>
                  <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-600 mb-3">
                    Comprehensive Wikipedia page listing digital library projects, updated regularly. Includes both legal and community resources.
                  </Text>
                  <a
                    href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_digital_library_projects"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-base-700 bg-base-200 border border-base-300 rounded hover:bg-base-300 hover:border-accent-300 transition-colors"
                  >
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
