                  <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-600 mb-3">
                    Massive digital library with millions of books and articles. Frequently changes domains due to legal issues.
                  </Text>
                  <Text tag="p" variant="textXS" class="text-base-500 italic mb-3">
                    Note: Check current domain via Wikipedia or search engines as URLs change frequently.
                  </Text>
                  <a
                    href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Z-Library"
